@1439 = ~Drow Adamantite Dagger +3~
@1440 = ~Most drow carry daggers forged from adamantite alloy and reinforced with enchantments. Some are even coated with one of the several types of drow poisons, allowing them to be well-prepared to deal with assassins, a constant danger in drow society. Of course, the daggers are also used just as frequently by the assassins themselves...

