@2245 = ~When asked about her past, KEIRIA SILVERSTRING divulges that she comes from a musically talented family. Both her father and mother are long time members of the Harpers. Keiria has gained much of her outlook on life from her parents and their association with the Harpers. She is a very talented songstress and actress. She has appeared in venues from Silverymoon to Athkatla. However, aside from her charming personality, half-elven beauty and long flowing red locks, Keiria is also a very adept fighter and can hold her own in any battle. She even prefers the life of adventuring to life on the stage. She says it makes her feel alive to experience adventure and danger.~
